poplist <- list()
idlist <- list()
fitlist <- list()
for (i in 1:nsims) {
    tmppop <- list()
    tmpid <- list()
    tmpfit <- list()
    
    for (j in 1:length(unique(filtered$type))) {
        data0 <- filtered %>% filter(simulation == i, type == unique(filtered$type)[j])
        
        all <- fit_saemix(data0 = data0)
        
        tmppop[[j]] <-  all$popCI
        tmpid[[j]] <-  all$idpar %>% mutate(id = unique(data0$id))
        tmpfit[[j]] <- all$fits
    }
    poplist[[i]] <- bind_rows(tmppop)
    idlist[[i]] <- bind_rows(tmpid)
    fitlist[[i]] <- bind_rows(tmpfit)
}
